1956;;Behind the High Wall;;American;;Abner Biberman;;Tom Tully, John Gavin;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Behind_the_High_Wall;;Inmates pull a prison break, taking the warden and another prisoner as hostages. But when the car gets into a crash, killing the others, the warden makes off with the gang's loot and places the blame on the other hostage.